snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS: Birth By Sleep - Gamescom Trailer
snippet.description:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kingdomhearts

[Square Enix]
Facebook: http://facebook.com/SquareEnix
Twitter: http://twitter.com/Square_Enix_EU
Website: http://www.square-enix.com/eu/en/


Unlock the untold origins of KINGDOM HEARTS! 
Play as new characters Ventus, Terra or Aqua and embark on an amazing adventure taking you to the magical Disney worlds of Snow White, Cinderella, Lilo & Stitch and more, to defeat the darkness with awesome powers and the help of many new friends!

Kingdom Hearts Birth By Sleep

September 10th 2010
